/// Grants a user line-wide access to the Pharmacy features on the MOBILE app
/// (scanner + add-stock + sync). Managed from the web Medicine > Config >
/// "Mobile Access" tab. Without a row here, a logged-in mobile user is blocked
/// from the pharmacy endpoints (403) — protects medicine data from unauthorized
/// modification. One row per (line, user).
